              "id": "40927445-5a0a-4401-9563-cf8c72e9a3ff",
              "role": "ai",
              "content": "pdf\n# Invoice Management System Q&A (For PDF) ## Invoice‐Related ### Q: How do I create a new invoice. Dashboard → Click Invoice module card. ### Q: Show me all pending invoices A: 1. Navigate to Invoices (via nav bar or Invoice Options → VIEW). A: Dashboard shows real‐time Total Revenue , Total Invoices , Pending Payments , and Total Products in the top stats grid. ### Q: How do I mark an invoice as paid. Go to Invoices. Find the pending invoice. Click Mark as Paid in its Action column. ### Q: Can you search for invoice INV-0001. Go to Invoices. Type the invoice ID or customer name in the search bar. ### Q: How do I add a discount to an invoice. Create/edit an invoice.",
